title: The People’s Champ, Paul Wall joins the show!
description:
Jalen & Jacoby talk to the People’s Champ, Paul Wall about his upcoming album "Start 2 Finish". Wall gloats about the Rockets’ Jalen Green and why he’s all in on the Astros being the villains of Major League Baseball. What it do! Also, we breakdown the end of that Bucks/76ers game. Giannis blocks Embiid to get the big win, but will it be Philly that gets the last laugh in the end?  Plus, LeBron sits out as Luka’s triple-double fuels the Mavericks blow out win over the Lakers. Lakers now fall out of the play-in tournament. Will we see a run by the Lakers or should LA throw in the towel? All that and much more.
